    np.random.seed(43)

tt = np.linspace(0, 10, 1000)
ind = np.sort(np.random.choice(range(tt.size), 48))
t = tt[ind]
gp = GP(PERkernel(η1=1, η3=5.2, η4=0.8), tt)
s = gp.sample()
y = s[ind] + np.random.normal(0, 0.1, size=t.size)
err = np.random.uniform(0.1, 0.3, size=t.size)
plt.plot(tt, s);
plt.errorbar(t, s[ind], err, fmt='o');
